INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (19,3,'2012-04-25 00:26:59','2012-04-25 00:26:59','<a href=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/features/319/welcome/attachment/elyse-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-322\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-322\" title=\"Elyse!\" src=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Elyse-Andrews-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" /></a>Hi! I’m Elyse Andrews, the founder of the Somerville Beat.\r\n\r\nAs the writer, editor and photographer behind the Beat, I\'m using what I\'ve learned in my <a href=\"http://elyseandrews.com/\">decade-long career</a> to intimately cover Somerville’s active food scene, its booming creative economy and everything in between. I landed in Somerville nearly five years ago and while I’ve loved it the whole time, it seems that there’s never been a better time to be here than right now.\r\n\r\nThe Somerville Beat is all about providing residents of the city and beyond with a local, in-depth perspective on the unique stories and events happening in town. Somerville is alive with innovative and passionate people working to build a strong community and we’re proud to be a part of that.\r\n\r\nThe Somerville Beat’s website was created by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/m_swartz\">Mike Swartz</a>, who was responsible for the <a href=\"http://upstatement.com/\">Boston Globe’s recent redesign</a>. It uses responsive design technology to deliver the highest-quality original content on every type of device you can think of.\r\n\r\nThis intersection of cutting-edge journalism and design, combined with our perspectives as Somerville residents, means the Beat provides an experience readers won’t find anywhere else.\r\n\r\nI hope you enjoy what you find here and thank you for reading!\r\n\r\nSee you around town,\r\nElyse\r\n\r\nP.S. Connect with the Beat on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomervilleBeat\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/somervillebeat\">Facebook</a> to stay on top of the latest news, features and exclusive content!','About','','publish','open','open','','about','','','2012-10-14 20:02:55','2012-10-15 00:02:55','',0,'http://localhost/?page_id=19',0,'page','',7);
