INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (272,4,'2012-05-09 07:00:35','2012-05-09 07:00:35','A few weeks ago, I went to the dog park with my friend where I encountered Zeus, a massive mastiff. He weighs upward of 200 pounds, but he\'s as docile and friendly as can be. And he does tricks! Well, he sits on benches pretty well.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Zeus1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-274\" title=\"Zeus\" src=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Zeus1-1024x894.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"558\" /></a><small><em style=\"text-align: right;\">Photo by Mike Swartz</em></small></p>\r\nWe saw him again this weekend in Union Square and he and his owner Peter were kind enough to pose for a photo. Perhaps he and <a href=\"http://www.somervillebeat.com/features/have-you-seen-pepper/\">Pepper</a> can be friends?\r\n\r\n<em>*If you know of a dog larger than Zeus, let me know, I\'d love to interview them!</em>','Meet Zeus, Largest Dog in Somerville*','','publish','open','open','','zeus-large-dog-somerville','','','2012-10-15 16:25:38','2012-10-15 20:25:38','',0,'http://www.somervillebeat.com/?p=272',0,'post','',7);
