INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (277,4,'2012-05-07 07:00:11','2012-05-07 07:00:11','<a href=\"http://www.somervillebeat.com/things-to-do/somerville-open-studios-5-4-5-6/\">Somerville Open Studios</a> is one of my favorite weekends and this year did not disappoint. We started our day at <a href=\"http://fringeunion.com/\">Fringe Union</a>, a huge (more than 4,00 square foot) creative co-working space in Union Square. The building houses photographers, <a href=\"http://www.prettythingsbeertoday.com/wp/\">Pretty Things</a> beer, the <a href=\"http://cuppow.com/\">Cuppow</a> creators and many other innovative businesses.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Fringe-Table.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-280\" title=\"Fringe Table\" src=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Fringe-Table-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></a>\r\n\r\nFringe is a big, rambling space and not long after entering, we ran into Mike Dacey, the man behind <a href=\"http://repeatpress.wordpress.com/\">Repeat Press</a>, a custom letterpress printing shop. He prints everything from business cards and wedding invitations to restaurant materials and posters.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Fringe-Dacey.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-278\" title=\"Fringe Dacey\" src=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Fringe-Dacey-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></a>\r\n\r\nI also had the pleasure of meeting <a href=\"http://keenaphoto.com/\">Justin Keena</a>, a photographer with a passion for skateboarding. His studio had a great blend of old and new and we had a great time chatting about our respective weddings in New Hampshire.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Fringe-Justin.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-279\" title=\"Fringe Justin\" src=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Fringe-Justin-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></a><small><em style=\"text-align: right;\">Photos by Mike Swartz</em></small></p>\r\nFringe is full of creative energy and every time I go there I meet so many interesting, creative people doing really cool stuff right in Somerville.\r\n\r\n[google-map-sc]','Open Studios: Fringe Union','','publish','open','open','','open-studios-fringe-union','','','2012-10-15 16:24:31','2012-10-15 20:24:31','',0,'http://www.somervillebeat.com/?p=277',0,'post','',2);
