INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1527,4,'2012-08-14 07:00:12','2012-08-14 11:00:12','<em>Boston Magazine</em> recently released its annual <a href=\"http://www.bostonmagazine.com/boston/best-of/\">Best Of Boston 2012</a> issue, honoring several Somerville businesses in various categories. I was pleased to see the magazine recognize neighborhoods all over town, not just in the usual hot spots (though I think there are always more small squares and businesses that deserve to be honored). Congratulations to all of the Somerville businesses that were featured!\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<h3>Arts &amp; Entertainment</h3>\r\nBowling: <a href=\"http://www.flatbreadcompany.com/\">Sacco\'s Bowl Haven</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Saccos.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1531\" title=\"Sacco\'s\" src=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Saccos.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"610\" /></a>\r\n<h3>Oddball</h3>\r\nAlternative to Spotify: <a href=\"http://www.highlandkitchen.com/\">Highland Kitchen\'s</a> Jukebox <a href=\"http://blog.bozzuto.com/2012/05/highland-kitchen-offers-great-food-service-and-atmosphere-in-boston/\"><em>(Read my review here.)</em></a>\r\nHipster Invention: <a href=\"http://www.cuppow.com/\">Cuppow</a>\r\nSpot to Get Schooled: <a href=\"http://artisansasylum.com/\">Artisan\'s Asylum</a> (<em>sculpture made by <a href=\"http://www.somervillebeat.com/features/364/open-studios-skunk/\">Skunk</a> pictured below)</em>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/untitled4.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-369\" title=\"Robot!\" src=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/untitled4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3>Restaurants &amp; Food</h3>\r\nBartender: Sam Treadway, <a href=\"http://www.backbarunion.com/\">Backbar</a> <a href=\"http://www.somervillebeat.com/food/264/backbar-craft-cocktails-union-square/\"><em>(Read my review here.)</em></a>\r\nNeighborhood Restaurant, Davis Square: <a href=\"http://fivehorsestavern.com/\">Five Horses Tavern</a>\r\nNeighborhood Restaurant, Union Square: <a href=\"http://www.theindo.com/\">The Independent</a> <a href=\"http://www.somervillebeat.com/food/935/the-independent-serves-up-delicious-food-and-drinks/\"><em>(Read my review here.)</em></a>\r\nWine Program: <a href=\"http://bergamotrestaurant.com/\">Bergamot</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/BB-back-word-e1336223414650.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-267\" title=\"BB back word\" src=\"http://somervillebeat.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/BB-back-word-e1336223414650-764x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"857\" /></a>\r\n<h3>Shopping</h3>\r\nVintage Clothing: <a href=\"http://artifaktori.com/\">Artifaktori</a>\r\n\r\nP.S. The <em>Improper Bostonian</em> also published a Boston\'s Best issue that honored several Somerville businesses earlier this year. <a href=\"http://www.somervillebeat.com/features/1144/improper-bostonian-ranks-the-best-of-somerville/\">See the list here.</a>\r\n\r\n[google-map-sc]','Best Of Somerville via Boston Magazine','','publish','open','open','','best-of-somerville-via-boston-magazine','','','2012-10-15 16:21:46','2012-10-15 20:21:46','',0,'http://www.somervillebeat.com/?p=1527',0,'post','',1);
