-7 p.m.\n65 Holland St.</li>\n	<li>\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.somervilletheatreonline.com/somerville-theatre/\">Somerville Theatre</a></h4>\nAwkward Compliment\'s comedy night\n55 Davis Square</li>\n</ul>\n<a name=\"friday\"></a>\n<h2 class=\"hdr-box\">Friday</h2>\n<ul class=\"grid\">\n	<li>\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.ballsquarefinewines.com/\">Ball Square Fine Wines &amp; Liquors</a></h4>\nFree wine, beer and liquor tastings\n716 Broadway</li>\n	<li>\n<h4><a href=\"http://somervillebeat.com/food/2296/coffee-goes-counter-culture-at-new-training-center/\">Counter Culture Coffee</a></h4>\nCuppings (coffee tastings) at 10 a.m.\n374 Somerville Ave.</li>\n	<li>\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.davesfreshpasta.com/\">Dave\'s Fresh Pasta</a></h4>\nFree wine tastings\n225 Elm St.</li>\n	<li>\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.downtownwineandspirits.com/\">Downtown Wine &amp; Spirits</a></h4>\nFree wine, beer and liquor tastings\n225 Elm St.</li>\n	<li>\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.joshuatreesomerville.com/\">Joshua Tree</a></h4>\nDJ Cam\n256 Elm St.</li>\n	<li>\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.orleansrestaurant.com/\">Orleans</a></h4>\nDJ starting at 10 p.m.\n$5 appetizers and $1 oysters Monday-Friday from 3 p.m.-7 p.m.\n65 Holland St.</li>\n	<li>\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.savmorspirits.com/\">Sav-Mor Spirits</a></h4>\nFree wine, beer and liquor tastings\n15 McGrath Highway</li>\n</ul>\n<a name=\"saturday\"></a>\n<h2 class=\"hdr-box\">Saturday</h2>\n<ul class=\"grid\">\n	<li>\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.davesfreshpasta.com/\">Dave\'s Fresh Pasta</a></h4>\nFree wine tastings\n225 Elm St.</li>\n	<li>\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.joshuatreesomerville.com/\">Joshua Tree</a></h4>\nDJ El Sid\n256 Elm St.</li>\n	<li>\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.orleansrestaurant.com/\">Orleans</a></h4>\nKaraoke at 10 p.m.\n$5 appetizers and $1 oysters Monday-Friday from 3 p.m.-7 p.m.\n65 Holland St.</li>\n</ul>','Seven Nights in Somerville','','inherit','open','open','','2461-autosave','','','2012-11-04 16:57:03','2012-11-04 21:57